вЂњWhat?вЂќ

вЂњPay back the three thousand.вЂќ

вЂњWhere can we get it from? I say, I have two thousand. Ivan will give you
another thousandвЂ”that makes three. Take it and pay it back.вЂќ

вЂњAnd when would you get it, your three thousand? YouвЂ™re not of age,
