вЂњTo father?вЂќ

вЂњYes, to father first. Ask him for three thousand.вЂќ

вЂњBut, Mitya, he wonвЂ™t give it.вЂќ

вЂњAs though he would! I know he wonвЂ™t. Do you know the meaning of despair,
Alexey?вЂќ

вЂњYes.вЂќ

вЂњListen. Legally he owes me nothing. IвЂ™ve had it all from him, I know
