are not listening. Do you know, you are not at all well this evening? I
know you went yesterday to that doctor ... well, what about your health?
What did the doctor say?вЂќ

вЂњFool!вЂќ Ivan snapped out.

вЂњBut you are clever, anyway. You are scolding again? I didnвЂ™t ask out of
sympathy. You neednвЂ™t answer. Now rheumatism has come in againвЂ”вЂќ

вЂњFool!вЂќ repeated Ivan.

вЂњYou keep saying the same thing; but I had such an attack of rheumatism
last year that I remember it to this day.вЂќ

вЂњThe devil have rheumatism!вЂќ

вЂњWhy not, if I sometimes put on fleshly form? I put on fleshly form and I
take the consequences. Satan _sum et nihil humanum a me alienum puto_.вЂќ

вЂњWhat, what, Satan _sum et nihil humanum_ ... thatвЂ™s not bad for the
devil!вЂќ

вЂњI am glad IвЂ™ve pleased you at last.вЂќ

вЂњBut you didnвЂ™t get that from me.вЂќ Ivan stopped suddenly, seeming struck.
вЂњThat never entered my head, thatвЂ™s strange.вЂќ

вЂњ_CвЂ™est du nouveau, nвЂ™estвЂђce pas?_ This time IвЂ™ll act honestly and explain
