dreams are sometimes seen not by writers, but by the most ordinary people,
officials, journalists, priests.... The subject is a complete enigma. A
statesman confessed to me, indeed, that all his best ideas came to him
when he was asleep. Well, thatвЂ™s how it is now, though I am your
hallucination, yet just as in a nightmare, I say original things which had
not entered your head before. So I donвЂ™t repeat your ideas, yet I am only
your nightmare, nothing more.вЂќ

вЂњYou are lying, your aim is to convince me you exist apart and are not my
nightmare, and now you are asserting you are a dream.вЂќ

вЂњMy dear fellow, IвЂ™ve adopted a special method toвЂђday, IвЂ™ll explain it to
you afterwards. Stay, where did I break off? Oh, yes! I caught cold then,
only not here but yonder.вЂќ

вЂњWhere is yonder? Tell me, will you be here long? CanвЂ™t you go away?вЂќ Ivan
exclaimed almost in despair. He ceased walking to and fro, sat down on the
