specialist who cures noses. If you go to Paris, heвЂ™ll look at your nose; I
can only cure your right nostril, heвЂ™ll tell you, for I donвЂ™t cure the
left nostril, thatвЂ™s not my speciality, but go to Vienna, there thereвЂ™s a
specialist who will cure your left nostril. What are you to do? I fell
