вЂњWhat tortures? Ah, donвЂ™t ask. In old days we had all sorts, but now they
have taken chiefly to moral punishmentsвЂ”вЂthe stings of conscienceвЂ™ and all
that nonsense. We got that, too, from you, from the softening of your
