get the character of that thinker who lay across the road.вЂќ

вЂњWhat did he lie on there?вЂќ

вЂњWell, I suppose there was something to lie on. You are not laughing?вЂќ

вЂњBravo!вЂќ cried Ivan, still with the same strange eagerness. Now he was
listening with an unexpected curiosity. вЂњWell, is he lying there now?вЂќ

вЂњThatвЂ™s the point, that he isnвЂ™t. He lay there almost a thousand years and
then he got up and went on.вЂќ

вЂњWhat an ass!вЂќ cried Ivan, laughing nervously and still seeming to be
