вЂњMuch more than that. I havenвЂ™t got a pencil and paper or I could work it
out. But he got there long ago, and thatвЂ™s where the story begins.вЂќ

вЂњWhat, he got there? But how did he get the billion years to do it?вЂќ

вЂњWhy, you keep thinking of our present earth! But our present earth may
