вЂњFool, how stupid!вЂќ cried Ivan.

вЂњMy dear friend, I only wanted to amuse you. But I swear thatвЂ™s the
genuine Jesuit casuistry and I swear that it all happened word for word as
IвЂ™ve told you. It happened lately and gave me a great deal of trouble. The
